Runs well on my Samsung GS7 but will not load on my Nexus 9 tablet. A decent adventure game where instead of a boss to fight to complete a level, you answer math questions. You also need to answer enough questions in a limited time to get enough points to unlock the next level. My daughter was very engaged by the game and was trying very hard to answer as many math problems as possible in the time frame. Two complaints: my daughter does not want to play a boy character and wishes she could choose a girl instead. Second, movement is a little tricky, touch-to-move would be easier than a virtual joystick.
replyContent: Thank you for playing Math Land. We are happy you found it useful. We take note of the complaints and will try to improve it in future updates.
